 
<p>
*   To call this a "culture" war is to understate its true meaning and
   potential danger. Those of us who still believe in separating church
   and state, guarding reproductive rights, ensuring racial equality,
   ending gun violence, and protecting democracy must understand that much
   of the Republican Party now stands for the 
<a href="https://robertreich.substack.com/p/the-republican-party-god-guns-forced">exact opposite of these
   values.</a>*
   
 